...if you haven't figured it out yet, Joey is the key component of my wedding tackle, and he needs a new last name! Between now and midnight October 31st, 2003... I will be taking requests for last names for my little buddy. Submissions will be judged and awarded a placement: 1st, 2nd, 3rd, Honorable Mention. The First Place winner will receive 5 questpoints and the dubious honor of having given my uhh... a last name. Second place winner will receive 3 qps. Third place winners will receive 2 qps, and Honorable Mentions (there may be more the one) will receive 1 qp and a pat on the arse. So! Get those creative juices flowing, get mail sent to me with your suggestions and then get RPing, since that's why you're all here anyways...

